name: Short title
text:
ARTICLE 1.  GENERAL PROVISIONS
 
Note
 
  Article heading reenacted by L 2015, c 77, pt of §1.
 
 
     §576B-101  Short title.  This chapter may be cited as the Uniform Interstate Family Support Act. [L 2015, c 77, pt of §1]
 
Note
 
  This section is new.  Former §576B-101 renumbered as §576B-102.
